# RNRepo's local prebuilt-artifact cache must never perturb the OTA runtime-version fingerprint
# (app.config.ts `runtimeVersion: { policy: 'fingerprint' }`, read by mobile-ota.yml). Whether a
# covered module is fetched prebuilt or compiled from source is a build accelerator, NOT a change to
# the native surface a shipped binary presents — so it must not change the fingerprint or old
# binaries would stop receiving OTA updates.
**/.rnrepo-cache/**/*
